            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We have been at Rims International School, Andheri West, Lokhandwala, Mumbai since its founding and could not be happier. My Son Jash in the IGCSE curriculum and planning to do As / A levels has had excellent and caring teachers and has thrived under their guidance. Every year they truly get to know him as an individual and push him to meet high academic standards. They consistently differentiate learning in the small size classroom and challenge students with the international rigorous curriculum but still find lots of ways to make learning fun and exciting. There is a ton of creativity in their approach and a very strong visual and performing art element in the curriculum which is important to us. The Cambridge curriculum is also a huge plus and it truly imparts Science to the students. I can’t say enough good things about the school and its wonderful parent community.",
