          "reviewBody": "I’ll give 5 stars to RIMS International School for various reasons. Firstly for the support they provide to their student in every aspect in shaping their career. Secondly for the well organised classes, teachers and staff. Teachers always support to level up the performance. I’m thankful and much obliged to RIMS International School.",
