            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "RIMS is an amazing learning zone where the faculty do an\nunimaginable job at helping your child to learn from any corner of the world and this prestigious institute also facilitates offline learning with an effective curriculum and an interactive environment . The principal ,board of directors and the admissions and BBA incharge have done a magnolious and a transcendent piece of work at establishing this institute and offering it to its fellow inquisitive and eccentric learners an efficient learning environment and a  pliant curriculum for the students well being\n\nTo conclude , RIMS should be the first choice for your child where your child discovers his utmost learning potential",
